{"tid":1211601,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"[AOE] 住poly hall嘅同學入一入黎","createTime":"2019-06-12T16:06:01.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-13T11:47:15.000Z","uid":10533,"like":186,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"9c9e0269c97593eabdae91175464e63b437c575e","tid":1211601,"uid":10533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T16:06:01.000Z","msg":"啱啱出完金鐘返hall 附近搵嘢食<br />\n打算去麥記食個蜜汁豬頸肉飯<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n食食下個廚走出黎指住電視問我地有冇出到去 有三千幾蚊收fat fat<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n當堂得啖笑 好彩都有在場人士開口屌鳩返佢轉頭<br />\n有幾個同學本身打算食都頭也不回咁走左<br />\n<br />\n我就以後都唔會再食架啦<br />\n希望咁多位住hall嘅朋友食之前都好好考慮一下<br />\n麥記係poly hall都幾受歡迎 冇左hall呢條水我諗佢都收得皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">廣傳plz!!!</span></span>"},{"pid":"d036fa4a67b8010362442d7f88fbc3eafabfaf35","tid":1211601,"uid":10533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T16:08:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1f84ed86554115a3e54f050c058c1ccb18412f59","tid":1211601,"uid":255098,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T16:08:55.000Z","msg":"推到佢無生意"},{"pid":"5b56382af9028b9d9ed1c92d14ee864c3e04832a","tid":1211601,"uid":10533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T16:10:15.000Z","msg":"Pish"},{"pid":"3baac28a3dae035d765d417a9d52b83372c91c72","tid":1211601,"uid":10533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T16:15:47.000Z","msg":"Pish"},{"pid":"576afc9ecca1001c24b0aeb67c1b70feacc393e3","tid":1211601,"uid":10533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T16:29:48.000Z","msg":"Pish"},{"pid":"8a9721c6716a37099f4cb027fa8d796f86fa1ffd","tid":1211601,"uid":156326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T16:30:59.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":